measurements.description:
Fifty-nine well arranged flowers on five arching, 75-cm average, inflorescences well presented above gracefully arching leaves;
	 63-cm x 104-cm plant grown in 17-cm one-gallon plastic pot in a mixture of coconut chips, perlite, bark;
	 dorsal sepal hooded, sepals and petals pale yellow-green overlaid dusty rose, irregular cordovan spots and stripes;
	 lip side lobes light yellow, irregular cordovan markings, midlobe white, irregular burgundy-red markings, keel light yellow, sparsely spotted burgundy red;
	 column cream, inferior surface randomly spotted maroon, superior surface overlaid rose, anther cap white;
	 substance firm; texture matte;  also awarded an AM, #20225409.
